A Suffolk/USA Today Poll, just out, states, “50% of Americans AGREE that Robert Mueller’s investigation is a Witch Hunt.” @MSNBC Very few think it is legit!
Independents are split, with 52% agreeing it’s a witch hunt and 42% disagreeing.
Trump’s rhetorical campaign against the “witch hunt” has been ramping up over recent weeks.
